snippet.textDisplay:
Hands down!! 
Coke Studio Pakistan is the ultimate class and the richness of music and songwriting from pakistani artists is the ultimate ART. 

I found this one in my saved playlist when I was looking for my favorite coke studio versions. I can’t believe I still can hum to this song, line by line, rhythm by rhythm. One in my bucket list, I will sit in-front of such musical magicians on live and delve into their world. ❤ from Nepal.
